 1. Thank you push me off a cliff let me see the whole sky.感谢你将我推下悬崖让我看清整片天空。

2. To avoid the reality person, the future will be more ideal.回避现实的人，未来将更不理想。

3. Apart from the freshness of the beginning, companionship and understanding are more important.除去一开始的新鲜感，陪伴与懂得更加重要。

4. life is the flower for which love is the honey.生命如花，爱情是蜜。

5. Finger rift,twisted in the love. 如果你为着错过夕阳而哭泣，那么你就要错群星了。

6. Learning to ignore things is one of the great paths to inner peace.学会忽略，是通向内心平静的康庄大路。 